    "description": "The small city of Felsde, where Oliver and his family currently reside, is a lovely and endearing place. An elderly man came to the family one day looking for assistance. He had a &quot;message&quot; to deliver, but the distance was too great for him. If Oliver could deliver it, he would offer him and his family enormous wealth, but only under the condition that Oliver not read the contents of the package.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/acf0b16307969c678118e42f4ca24f3e.poster.avif?t=1670420123\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/acf0b16307969c678118e42f4ca24f3e.webm?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/acf0b16307969c678118e42f4ca24f3e.mp4?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Oliver accepted the call to adventure despite having never left his hometown. His greatest challenge will come from this new endeavor, because he is not well prepared for the dangers that can be found when being away from home. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/7a6a63350fe49f2f15e54e341d315eae.poster.avif?t=1670420123\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/7a6a63350fe49f2f15e54e341d315eae.webm?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/7a6a63350fe49f2f15e54e341d315eae.mp4?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>He discovered a few characters on the way to deliver the package that might clarify the true request. Having a collection of books could aid in deciphering this message without having to read it, as they all provide him with sufficient knowledge to understand the dangers of carrying something he is unfamiliar with.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/bf8c9f6e03a69004cf9216dc3ac4315d.poster.avif?t=1670420123\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/bf8c9f6e03a69004cf9216dc3ac4315d.webm?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/bf8c9f6e03a69004cf9216dc3ac4315d.mp4?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Oliver holds a special place in his heart for his grandmother because he has always regarded her as a source of knowledge and compassion. The supernatural assistance Oliver received from his grandmother after she passed away allowed him to move more quickly and jump higher.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/3982fe50fb305865abf1b7390a9cef0e.poster.avif?t=1670420123\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/3982fe50fb305865abf1b7390a9cef0e.webm?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/3982fe50fb305865abf1b7390a9cef0e.mp4?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Navigate vibrant but difficult levels<br>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/69286facb4cbd7e0e42769d8c658cd95.poster.avif?t=1670420123\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/69286facb4cbd7e0e42769d8c658cd95.webm?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/69286facb4cbd7e0e42769d8c658cd95.mp4?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Easily control the main character<br>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/dd227d28df91b3f2bdc66d97f7d9ac86.poster.avif?t=1670420123\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/dd227d28df91b3f2bdc66d97f7d9ac86.webm?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/dd227d28df91b3f2bdc66d97f7d9ac86.mp4?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Complete amazing quests<br>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/1f5f45a0fec00739dbe8c7f0a05ae430.poster.avif?t=1670420123\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/1f5f45a0fec00739dbe8c7f0a05ae430.webm?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240230/extras/1f5f45a0fec00739dbe8c7f0a05ae430.mp4?t=1670420123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
